Commands to set up and run project

## Create .venv

```bash
python -m venv .venv
```

To active:

## Powershell

```bash
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
```

## Command Prompt

```bash
.venv\Scripts\activate.bat
```

## Update pip

```bash
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
```

## Installing FastAPI

```bash
pip install fastapi uvicorn
```

## Command to run FastAPI

```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload
```